Grok editor/terminal themes
===========================

This repository packages Grok Build color palettes for Ghostty, Helix, and
Sublime Text / TextMate.

Upstream (color palettes and TextMate themes)
---------------------------------------------

  Project:  Grok Build (xai-org/grok-build)
  URL:      https://github.com/xai-org/grok-build
  License:  Apache License 2.0
  Copyright 2023-2026 SpaceXAI

  Canonical TUI palettes:
    crates/codegen/xai-grok-pager-render/src/theme/grokday.rs
    crates/codegen/xai-grok-pager-render/src/theme/groknight.rs

  Syntax themes (copied into sublime/):
    crates/codegen/xai-grok-pager-render/assets/grok-day.tmTheme
    crates/codegen/xai-grok-pager-render/assets/grok-night.tmTheme
    crates/codegen/xai-grok-pager-render/assets/tokyo-night.tmTheme

Derivative works in this repository
-----------------------------------

  ghostty/   — 16-color Ghostty terminal themes mapped from the TUI palettes
               (includes light-theme ANSI white contrast fix for external tools)
  helix/     — Helix editor theme ports (tree-sitter scopes + UI chrome)

